### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AI-MSHM  –  Check-in & Prediction Endpoints
###  Base prefixes:
###    /api/v1/checkin/
###    /api/v1/predictions/
###
###  DAILY FLOW:
###    Morning:   start session → POST morning data → submit HRV → submit session
###    Evening:   start session → POST evening data → submit HRV → submit session
###    After evening submit: prediction is auto-queued via Celery
###    Weekly:    POST mFG hirsutism assessment
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl       = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType   = application/json
@accessToken   = PASTE_PATIENT_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

# These are set after "start session" calls below
@morningSessionId   = PASTE_AFTER_START
@eveningSessionId   = PASTE_AFTER_START


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  DASHBOARD — Today's Status
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get today's check-in status (call this when app opens)
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkin/today/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Returns:
# {
#   "morning_status": "pending|partial|complete|missed",
#   "evening_status": "pending|partial|complete|missed",
#   "completeness_pct": 33,
#   "streak_days": 5,
#   "missed_yesterday_morning": false,
#   "missed_yesterday_evening": false,
#   "morning_session_id": "<uuid>",
#   "evening_session_id": "<uuid>"
# }


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  MORNING CHECK-IN FLOW
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 1: Start morning session (call on screen open — idempotent)
# @name startMorning
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/session/start/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "period": "morning",
  "checkin_date": "2026-03-17"
}

### STEP 2: Auto-save morning data as sliders change
###         (call on every slider change — partial save, not complete)
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/morning/{{morningSessionId}}/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "fatigue_vas": 6.5,
  "pelvic_pressure_vas": 3.0,
  "psq_skin_sensitivity": 4.0,
  "psq_muscle_pressure_pain": 5.0,
  "psq_body_tenderness": 3.5
}

# Returns computed hyperalgesia_index and hyperalgesia_severity automatically:
# {
#   "hyperalgesia_index": 4.167,
#   "hyperalgesia_severity": "Mild",
#   ...
# }

### STEP 3: Mark session as partially saved (auto-save heartbeat)
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/session/{{morningSessionId}}/autosave/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### STEP 4: Submit HRV capture result (after rPPG camera session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/hrv/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "session_id": "{{morningSessionId}}",
  "hrv_sdnn_ms": 42.5,
  "hrv_rmssd_ms": 38.2,
  "skipped": false
}

### STEP 4b: Skip HRV capture
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/hrv/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "session_id": "{{morningSessionId}}",
  "skipped": true
}

### STEP 5: Complete morning session
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/session/{{morningSessionId}}/submit/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

# Returns DailyCheckinSummary — shows completeness_pct, morning_complete=true, etc.


### GET morning data for a session (for re-hydrating screen state)
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkin/morning/{{morningSessionId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  EVENING CHECK-IN FLOW
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### STEP 1: Start evening session
# @name startEvening
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/session/start/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "period": "evening",
  "checkin_date": "2026-03-17"
}

### STEP 2: Save evening data — Mastalgia + GAGS Acne + Bloating
###  GAGS cofactors applied server-side:
###    Forehead×2, R.Cheek×2, L.Cheek×2, Nose×1, Chin×1, Chest/Back×3
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/evening/{{eveningSessionId}}/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "breast_left_vas": 6.0,
  "breast_right_vas": 7.0,
  "mastalgia_side": "Bilateral",
  "mastalgia_quality": "Dull",
  "acne_forehead": 2,
  "acne_right_cheek": 1,
  "acne_left_cheek": 1,
  "acne_nose": 0,
  "acne_chin": 1,
  "acne_chest_back": 2,
  "bloating_delta_cm": 2.5,
  "unusual_bleeding": false
}

# Server returns computed values automatically:
# {
#   "breast_pain_avg": 6.5,
#   "cyclic_mastalgia_score": 6.5,        (avg×1 since avg≤7)
#   "breast_soreness_vas": 3.25,          (CMS/2, normalised to 0-10)
#   "mastalgia_severity": "Moderate",
#   "gags_score": 19,                     (2×2+1×2+1×2+0×1+1×1+2×3 = 4+2+2+0+1+6=15... )
#   "acne_severity_likert": 1.295,        (gags/44×3)
#   "acne_severity_label": "Moderate"
# }

### STEP 3: Complete evening session
###  → Triggers DailyCheckinSummary assembly
###  → Triggers Celery prediction task if morning also complete
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/session/{{eveningSessionId}}/submit/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### GET evening data (to restore screen state)
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkin/evening/{{eveningSessionId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  WEEKLY — mFG Hirsutism Assessment
###  9 body areas, 0–4 each
###  Total = sum of all 9 areas (max 36)
###  Severity: Normal 0–7 | Mild 8–16 | Moderate 17–24 | Severe ≥25
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Submit weekly hirsutism assessment
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkin/mfg/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "mfg_upper_lip": 2,
  "mfg_chin": 1,
  "mfg_chest": 1,
  "mfg_upper_back": 0,
  "mfg_lower_back": 1,
  "mfg_upper_abdomen": 2,
  "mfg_lower_abdomen": 2,
  "mfg_upper_arm": 0,
  "mfg_thigh": 1
}

# Server returns computed mfg_total_score=10, mfg_severity="Mild"

### Get latest mFG score
GET {{baseUrl}}/checkin/mfg/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


