### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SEVERITY REFERENCE SCALES
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###
###  DISEASE SEVERITY (all 6 diseases — from notebook):
###    0.00–0.19  → Minimal   (no clinical concern)
###    0.20–0.39  → Mild      (monitor — lifestyle guidance)
###    0.40–0.59  → Moderate  (alert — medical review recommended)
###    0.60–0.79  → Severe    (referral — specialist review required)
###    0.80–1.00  → Extreme   (urgent — immediate clinical intervention)
###
###  GAGS ACNE SEVERITY:
###    0          → None
###    1–18       → Mild
###    19–30      → Moderate
###    31–38      → Severe
###    >38        → Very Severe
###    (max raw = 44 using cofactors: forehead×2, cheeks×2, nose×1, chin×1, chest/back×3)
###
###  mFG HIRSUTISM:
###    0–7        → Normal
###    8–16       → Mild Hirsutism
###    17–24      → Moderate Hirsutism
###    ≥25        → Severe Hirsutism
###    (max = 36, 9 areas × 4 points each)
###
###  HYPERALGESIA INDEX (PSQ-3):
###    (psq_skin + psq_muscle + psq_tenderness) / 3
###    0–3.0      → Normal
###    3.01–6.0   → Mild
###    6.01–9.0   → Moderate
###    9.01–10    → Severe
###
###  CYCLIC MASTALGIA:
###    avg = (left + right) / 2
###    score = avg × weight (weight: 0 if avg=0, 1 if avg≤7, 2 if avg>7)
###    normalised breast_soreness_vas = min(score/2, 10)
###    Severity: None | Mild (avg≤3.5) | Moderate (avg≤7) | Severe (avg>7)
